{
  "name": "RPlog_Lynae_s_Homecoming",
  "title": "Lynae's Homecoming",
  "summary": "Returning to the Night Tavern in Noques Rasala on Caspar after fifteen years away, Dr. Lynae Cassius reunites with the former raider turned priest Axel Vrichten, who greets her with a warm embrace and a drink. The quiet homecoming swells into a gathering of dignitaries as the Sarians Crestian and Fleet Captain Drorq arrive, followed by the Jedi Tracer and her companions Etiel and Elana. Over warm, rum-spiked drinks the group falls into a wide-ranging conversation about faith, worship, and the mysterious Olumi Osahn sect that Axel serves as priest. Axel excuses himself to deliver a prayer at the darkest hour, leaving the others to debate the nature of belief and the figure of Tyler. The evening becomes a rich, convivial reunion of old friends and new acquaintances trading philosophy and warmth against the Caspian cold.",
